  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "nrVeE3oDH0tNFm9CX5stkYPKAaCrnePTkJZtrLHmoDg=",
    "originContent": "## Features",
    "translatedContent": "## 功能"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "MKgiWm+lHwu3geAcNcB2IzEkyuhM8ure1OX9iVcKHmY=",
    "originContent": "- **Real-time streaming** via FIFO pipe — text appears as Claude generates it",
    "translatedContent": "- **实时流式传输** 通过 FIFO 管道——文本在 Claude 生成时实时显示"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "Xq3g7CZFVZaxsX4Zc82Qve9XJr5cMB21awNoenCnCww=",
    "originContent": "- **6 tools**: Bash, Read, Edit, Write, Glob, Grep",
    "translatedContent": "- **6 种工具**：Bash、Read、Edit、Write、Glob、Grep"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "7HNurhUBeZ8LIKAfK41Kb1FweAp/AFmCXzQYAPu+B6M=",
    "originContent": "- **Tool chaining** — up to 25 tool calls per turn",
    "translatedContent": "- **工具链式调用**——每轮最多调用 25 次工具"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "pd+pvDfZDKoavZZnLXB9Ph3dqIPI/TrWpqpraeykZP4=",
    "originContent": "- **Permission prompting** — asks before running non-safe commands (`y/n/a`)",
    "translatedContent": "- **权限提示**——在运行不安全命令前询问（`y/n/a`）"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "ZWtQK4rRfAgX2G6MLMpSTQ7P+FNJC4MCroO815FIP9E=",
    "originContent": "- **CLAUDE.md loading** — reads project instructions from CLAUDE.md files up the directory tree",
    "translatedContent": "- **CLAUDE.md 加载**——从目录树中的 CLAUDE.md 文件读取项目说明"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "kTGh2aReJCkR8jtMpN6Q6kPF7pJCEjU8XDYFkl4WZNM=",
    "originContent": "- **Git-aware context** — branch, status, and recent commits in system prompt",
    "translatedContent": "- **Git 感知上下文**——分支、状态和最近提交在系统提示中显示"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "aCXPuZT2KuI2+d0lVbmR4Qz9aNC2qiKmejSBC7qOeiE=",
    "originContent": "- **Session save/resume** — auto-saves on exit, resume with `--resume <id>`",
    "translatedContent": "- **会话保存/恢复**——退出时自动保存，使用 `--resume <id>` 恢复"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "ekReIc69bWLCT8JmlrG96mRhOybGNkSEs0JH8xOnPp8=",
    "originContent": "- **Retry with backoff** — exponential retry on 429/529 rate limits",
    "translatedContent": "- **退避重试**——对 429/529 速率限制进行指数级重试"
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "ZaaNzduEmQ4X4dDLnKLxczhQfVvq4/2N0yPejUibOds=",
    "originContent": "- **Cost tracking** — per-turn and session totals",
    "translatedContent": "- **成本跟踪**——每轮和会话总成本"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "Rn8H42FSDtdH4tZixEEMu33AZZeqHo1Tj2I6HShQkkM=",
    "originContent": "- **Spinner** — with the original spinner verbs (Clauding, Flibbertigibbeting, etc.)",
    "translatedContent": "- **加载动画**——使用原始加载动词（Clauding、Flibbertigibbeting 等）"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "TRpr63+kcTxeyaYNkxUnwoM/YwU/Jvk8dM9uiDi05QA=",
    "originContent": "- **Slash commands** — `/help`, `/cost`, `/model`, `/clear`, `/save`, `/resume`, `/commit`, `/diff`",
    "translatedContent": "- **斜杠命令**——`/help`、`/cost`、`/model`、`/clear`、`/save`、`/resume`、`/commit`、`/diff`"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "8E5EeIs7GreSVyrSeTrfOkT76vy0Sw4Z593ZpdrXJPw=",
    "originContent": "- **Pipe mode** — `echo \"explain this\" | ./claude.sh`",
    "translatedContent": "- **管道模式**——`echo \"explain this\" | ./claude.sh`"
  },
